      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="reveal bg-white border-3 border-v13-black p-7 shadow-[6px_6px_0px_#D32F2F] transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0px_#D32F2F] hover:translate-x-[-2px] hover:translate-y-[-2px]">
